data.description: Gorgeous corner lot with 3 bed 2.5 bath located in the great Highgrove at Anderson Creek. Highly sought after Overhills school district and close to Ft Bragg & shopping centers. Spacious floorpan w/ LVP on first floor and in master bedroom. Enjoy a walk to the neighborhood pond & playground located right across the street. Schedule your showing today!
